    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Readers were riveted by Michael Finkel's below-deck account of his harrowing voyage with refugees fleeing Haiti. For many, it recalled similar hopeless journeys in history, art and literature. And parents of children with Asperger's wrote to emphasize the positive side of the syndrome.</p>
